title: Microsoft rolls out updates to the Office suite on Windows 10 Mobile
text:
Microsoft rolls out updates to the Office suite on Windows 10 Mobile 
Published By: WPCentral.com - Today 
Microsoft is rolling out updates to the Office Mobile suite on Windows 10 Mobile, with Word, Excel, PowerPoint and OneNote getting updated. ...
